<div class="txt-block" id="name-bio-text">
        <div class="name-trivia-bio-text">
                      <div class="inline" itemprop="description">
Steven Knight was born in 1959 in Marlborough, England. He is a writer and producer, known for <a href="/title/tt0765443?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk1">Eastern Promises</a> (2007), <a href="/title/tt2692904?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk2">Locke</a> (2013) and <a href="/title/tt2442560?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk3">Peaky Blinders</a> (2013).            <span class="see-more inline nobr-only">
                    <a href="/name/nm1140275/bio?ref_=nm_ov_bio_sm"
>See full bio</a> &raquo;
            </span>
</div>        </div>
</div>

                        
    <div id="name-born-info" class="txt-block">
        <h4 class="inline">Born:</h4> 
   
  <time datetime="1959-0-0" itemprop="birthDate">

     
<a href="/search/name?birth_year=1959&ref_=nm_ov_bth_year"
>1959</a>    
  </time>
            in
            <a href="/search/name?birth_place=Marlborough,+England,+UK&ref_=nm_ov_bth_place"
>Marlborough, England, UK</a>
    </div>

                        
                        
